com.vectorprint.configuration.annotation

Annotation Type SettingsField


  • @Documented
@Inherited
@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface SettingsField
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
    See Also:
    SettingsAnnotationProcessor

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean cache
      by default settings will be cached.
      Feature[] features
      You can add your own features to settings, these will be applied at the end of the decoration stack.
      boolean observable
      by default settings will not be observable.
      PreProcess[] preprocessors
      declare your preprocessors for key / value pairs
      boolean readonly
      by default settings will be read / write.
      String[] urls
      When urls are supplied properties will be loaded from it, using EnhancedMapBindingFactoryImpl.getDefaultFactory() for syntax.
